                "PlanID": 0,
                "PlanName": null,
                "ItemType": 9,
                "ItemID": 151542,
                "ItemTitle": "Cylance flagged components of Zoom on MacOS",
                "ReferenceID": null,
                "Body": "Changed Status from <b>Customer Responded</b> to <b>Waiting on Customer</b>.<br /><br />Hi,\r\nSorry for the challenges.  I added a system specific waiver.  The actions Eric completed should allow you to update and move forward. If the Update option does not work, I can send you the 2.1.1584 installation.  You may need to remove and reinstall Cylance if the issue persists.",
                "IsRichHtml": false,
                "UpdateType": 2,
                "NotifiedList": "Michael Porter <mike@UDel.Edu>",
                "IsPrivate": true,
                "IsParent": false,
                "Replies": [
                    {
                        "ID": 55217,
                        "Body": "Changed Status from &quot;<b>Waiting on Customer</b>&quot; to &quot;<b>Customer Responded</b>&quot;.<br/><br/>We've solved the Zoom problem now.  However, the update within Cylance is not working yet.  Perhaps sending me the 2.1.1584 installation would help?",
                        "IsRichHtml": false,
                        "CreatedUid": "e22201b5-7476-e911-a81a-000d3a1808ae",
