            {
                "ID": 422798,
                "CreatedUid": "f3463840-3ca5-e911-a81d-000d3a1808ae",
                "CreatedRefID": 4494,
                "CreatedFullName": "Eric Eckman",
                "CreatedFirstName": "Eric",
                "CreatedLastName": "Eckman",
                "CreatedByPicPath": null,
                "CreatedDate": "2021-04-21T18:32:00.793Z",
                "LastUpdatedDate": "2021-04-22T12:57:51.223Z",
                "ProjectID": 0,
                "ProjectName": null,
                "PlanID": 0,
                "PlanName": null,
                "ItemType": 9,
                "ItemID": 151542,
                "ItemTitle": "Cylance flagged components of Zoom on MacOS",
                "ReferenceID": null,
                "Body": "Changed Status from <b>In Process</b> to <b>Resolved</b>.<br /><br />Hi Mike,\r\n\r\nWe marked the file(s) as safe.  The &quot;aomhost&quot; files provided by Zoom seem to get flagged by Cylance often, there are 15 other variants of this we manually had to mark as &quot;safe&quot;, 6 of which Cylance later also marked as globally safe.\r\n\r\nHopefully you can just reinstall again and it&#39;ll work.  I&#39;m guessing you tried to install 5.6.3 yesterday because we had a different hash show up for that same filename.\r\n\r\nEric\r\n\r\nps  This often happens when vendors do something weird with their binaries when they build them.",
                "IsRichHtml": false,
                "UpdateType": 2,
                "NotifiedList": "Michael Porter <mike@UDel.Edu>, Craig Prettyman <craig@UDel.Edu>",
                "IsPrivate": false,
                "IsParent": false,
                "Replies": [
                    {
                        "ID": 55053,
                        "Body": "Changed Status from &quot;<b>Resolved</b>&quot; to &quot;<b>Customer Responded</b>&quot;.<br/><br/>Still failed to install.  Quarantined.",
                        "IsRichHtml": false,
                        "CreatedUid": "e22201b5-7476-e911-a81a-000d3a1808ae",
                        "CreatedRefID": 21,
                        "CreatedFullName": "Michael Porter",
                        "CreatedFirstName": "Michael",
                        "CreatedLastName": "Porter",
                        "CreatedByPicPath": null,
                        "CreatedDate": "2021-04-21T19:39:30.997Z"
                    },
                    {
                        "ID": 55119,
                        "Body": "And this morning also.  The file is an extra plugin that gets downloaded when I try to use backgrounds.  Also, please verify, specifically, that I am getting updates to Cylance.  Antivirus without updates is pointless.  Please see screenshots attached to tickets for why I wonder if updates are happening.",
                        "IsRichHtml": false,
